}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== *"GS728TPV2" and "REV1.0" are silkscreened on the main board. *"GO591-33012520A", "V0.1 VD" and "2018-03-05" are silkscreened on the power board. *"GS728TPv2-BUTTON" and "REV1.0" are silkscreened on the USB Button board. *"GS728TPv2-POE REV 1.0" is silkscreened on the PoE board. *"GS728TPP-CONSOLE" and "REV1.0" are silkscreened on the Console Extension board.
===Specifications=== *Processor: [[Realtek]] RTL8391M Multi-Layer Managed Switch :Controller with Embedded MIPS 34Kc @700MHz *Co-processor: Nuvoton MO516LDN to manage PoE *Microcontroller: TI MSP420FR2311 for fan control *Flash/RAM: 32MB (SPI NOR) Flash, 128MB RAM (DDR3L) *24x Gigabit PoE+ Ethernet ports *4x Gigabit SFP Slots *1x USB 1.1 port *190W PoE budget
